  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali55-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu “poṟiyiṉ yātta puṇarcci nōkki- yorumaik kēṇmaiyi ṉuṟukuṟai teḷintō - ḷarumai 
            cāṉṟa nāliraṇṭu vakaiyiṟ - perumai cāṉṟa viyalpiṉkaṭ” (to.po.111) ṭalaivi kūṟiyatu. eṉṟatu, 
            “orumaik kēṇmaiyiṉ uṟukuṟai - tāṉ avaḷeṉṉum vēṟṟumai-yillāta naṭpiṉālē tōḻi taṉakku vantu kūṟiya 
            kuṟaiyai; poṟiyiṉ yātta puṇarcci nōkkit teḷintōḷ- muṉṉart teyvappuṇarcci nikaḻntamai nōkki atu kāraṇattāṉ 
            muṭippatākat teḷinta talaivi; arumaicāṉṟa nāliraṇṭuvakaiyil - tāṉ muṉ arumaiyamaintu niṉṟanilaiyāṟ ṟalaivaṉ 
            taṉkaṇ nikaḻttiya meytoṭṭup payiṟaṉ mutaliya eṭṭiṉālē; perumaicāṉṟa iyalpiṉ kaṇṇum - taṉakku uḷatām 
            perumai kūṟutaṟku amaintatōr iyalpiṉ kaṇṇum; e-ṟu. itaṉāṟ pōnta poruḷ talaivaṉ ittuṇai iḷivantaṉa ceyyavum 
            yāṉ nāṇum maṭaṉum nīṅkiṟṟilēṉeṉṟu taṉ perumai tōḻikkuk kūṟutalāyiṟṟu”.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali55">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>miṉṉoḷi raviraṟa liṭaipōḻum peyalēpōṟ</l>
                <l>poṉṉakai takaivakir vakaineṟi vayaṅkiṭṭup</l>
                <l>pōḻiṭai yiṭṭa kamaḻnaṟum pūṅkōtai</l>
                <l>yiṉṉakai yilaṅkeyiṟṟut tēmoḻit tuvarccevvāy</l>
                <l>naṉṉutā ṉiṉakkoṉṟu kūṟuvāṅ kēḷiṉi;</l>
                <l rend="space">nilleṉa niṟuttā ṉiṟuttē vantu</l>
                <l>nutalu mukaṉun tōḷuṅ kaṇṇu</l>
                <l>miyaluñ collu nōkkupu niṉaii</l>
                <l>yaitēyn taṉṟu piṟaiyu maṉṟu</l>
                <l>maitīrn taṉṟu matiyu maṉṟu</l>
                <l>vēyamaṉ ṟaṉṟu malaiyu maṉṟu</l>
                <l>pūvamaṉ ṟaṉṟu cuṉaiyu maṉṟu</l>
                <l>mella viyalu mayilu maṉṟu</l>
                <l>collat taḷaruṅ kiḷiyu maṉṟu;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>aṉaiyaṉa palapā rāṭṭip paiyeṉa</l>
                <l>valaiyar pōlac cōrpata ṉoṟṟiyeṉ</l>
                <l>ṉeñcu nekiḻnta cevvi kāṇūup</l>
                <l>pulaiyar pōlap puṉka ṇōkkit</l>
                <l>toḻalun toḻutāṉ ṟoṭalun toṭṭāṉ</l>
                <l>kāḻvarai nillāk kaṭuṅkaḷi ṟaṉṉōṉ</l>
                <l>ṟoḻūun toṭūumavaṉ ṟaṉmai</l>
                <l>yēḻait taṉmaiyō villai tōḻi.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
